it.dc.bridge.om

Class ResponseMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.dc.bridge.om.ResponseMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CoAPResponseMessage

    public class ResponseMessage
extends java.lang.Object
implements CoAPResponseMessage
    The Class ResponseMessage is used in the AllJoyn message exchanges. It represents the CoAP response message and implements the CoAPResponseMessage interface.
    See Also:
    CoAPResponseMessage, CoAP.ResponseCode, Options
